snippet.title: Eidetus Pre-Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Eidetus is a strategic, team-based B.Y.O.H. (Build Your Own Hero) shooter set in a dystopian sci-fi landscape. Play as a Psypher channeling memories through psychic power while drawing from the deck of abilities you’ve assembled to defeat your opponents.

Website: https://www.eidetus.com

Follow for the latest news at:
https://twitter.com/eidetus
https://facebook.com/eidetus
https://instagram.com/eidetus
